Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:46.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\shad3}さらう彼の日　荒れし胸より
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:52.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\shad3}恐るるまま命は羽摶いて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:52.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\shad3}{\pos(320,330)}{\fs10}みこと
